sequenceDiagram
    participant L as Layout (setup_font)
    participant FP as FontProp cache
    participant E as lib/font engine
    L->>L: map font_weight and font_style to FontWeight and FontSlant
    L->>L: build FontStyleDesc (family, size_px, weight, slant)
    L->>FP: font_handle_matches_prop on cached handle
    alt cached handle matches
        FP-->>L: reuse font_handle (no resolve)
    else miss or stale
        L->>FP: font_prop_release_handle (release old ref)
        L->>E: font_resolve(font_ctx, style)
        E->>E: DB match, at-font-face, platform fallback, cache
        E-->>L: FontHandle (ref-counted)
        L->>FP: cache handle, set owns_font_handle
    end
    L->>E: font_get_metrics and font_get_normal_lh_split
    E-->>L: metrics
    L->>FP: populate space_width, ascender, descender, has_kerning
    Note right of E: later, per glyph during text flow
    L->>E: font_load_glyph (cmap, fallback, cache)
    L->>E: font_get_kerning(prev, cur)
